### 创建订单并支付 - 完整测试

@host=http://localhost:9528

### 1. 基本订单测试（单个商品）
POST {{host}}/v1/order/create-with-payment
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "user_test_001",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "prod_001",
      "skuId": "sku_001",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ],
  "shippingAddressId": "addr_456",
  "couponCode": "SUMMER2024",
  "paymentMethod": "wechat_pay",
  "remark": "请在下午送达"
}

